    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;Detecting Network Attachment allows hosts to assess if its existing addressing or routing configuration is valid for a newly connected network.  This document provides simple procedures for Detecting Network Attachment in IPv6 hosts, and procedures for routers to support such services. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
